snippet.title: Woodside - Official Trailer | WLG Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Take a tour of a creepy town in Woodside in this trailer for the upcoming third-person survival horror adventure game. Explore, investigate, and survive as Grace as she comes face to face with the supernatural terrors that plague a seemingly quaint British village. Woodside will be available on PC.
